snippet.title: The Adventures of Sam Carlisle - Teaser 1
snippet.description:
The Official Teaser trailer for THE ADVENTURES OF SAM CARLISLE: THE HUNT FOR THE LOST TREASURE. The game will be available 6 October 2017. Visit http://www.givitgames.co.za for more information.

Buy the game on Steam: http://store.steampowered.com/app/726500/The_Adventures_of_Sam_Carlisle_The_Hunt_for_the_Lost_Treasure/
